snippet.title: Chronotura | Indie Game Release Demo!
snippet.description:
Chronotura it’s a game about time travel to solve puzzles, but watch out! It gets tricky the more you advance. Inspire by the saga of portal, its playability is completely different since its perspective is isometric.

Try the demo now! It’s completely free and you can also contribute to development of the game by leaving a comment with your opinion.

Download: https://rfuchs.itch.io/chronotura

Follow me on my social media if you which to follow the progress of the game:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/RFuchss
Itch.io: https://rfuchs.itch.io

Subscribe to be updated in the progress of the game.

Drop a like and share, that helps a lot :)

Music: ＭＩＬＬＥＮＮＩＡＬＳ - Analog By Nature (ＭＩＬＬＥＮＮＩＡＬＳ by Analog By Nature (c) copyright 2018 Licensed under a Creative Commons Attribution (3.0) license.)
